  "title": "Visible Coords",
  "description": "Keep the coordinates always visible.",
  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><em><strong>Visible coords</strong></em></span></h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Welcome to the simplest mod you'll find on CurseForge. While it may not be the only mod out there, I hope it proves useful to you, just as it is for me. Despite its simplicity, this page is designed to provide you with all the necessary details. My only intention is for it to be useful and accompany you throughout your gaming experiences.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Features:</strong></span></h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">View coordinates on demand in your world</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Display coordinates upon starting a new world</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Show coordinates on a server</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Instructions:</strong></span></h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Press \"F3\" to toggle the visibility of coordinates</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Press \"C\" to show or hide the coordinates</span><br /><br />\n<h5><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>How it appears on the screen:</strong></span></h5>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/730/213/310/172/2023-09-17_06.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fwww.bisecthosting.com%252fModdyCraft\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/5e3de51b-bd49-4569-8be7-6ac3c5c9524d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"150\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
